data.title: Dari Alcantara - Women's Soccer
data.meta_description: Dari Alcantara (2) D  - AS A SENIOR (2011)NSCAA All-Region First Team…All-Sunshine State Conference First Team… Daktronics All-South Region Second
data.text:
AS A SENIOR (2011)

NSCAA All-Region First Team…All-Sunshine State Conference First Team… Daktronics All-South Region Second Team…Saint Leo Athlete of the Week…Competed in 17 games…Made 16 starts…Scored career-high 11 goals…Registered career-best five assists…Collected a career-best 27 points…Blasted 49 shots…Recorded career-best five game-winning goals…Was 1-for-1 in penalty kicks…Set career marks with three goals and seven points against Mercy (09/09/11).

AS A SENIOR (2010) - Red Shirt

Competed in two games before having season cut short due to injury...Tallied one goal in 180 minutes played.

AS A JUNIOR (2009)

Named All-Sunshine State Conference Second Team…She played and started in each of the Lions 15 contests…The defender totaled 17 shots, nine of which were on goal…She tallied her only goal of the season against Eckerd College (9/19/09)…She recorded her one assist against non conference opponent Clearwater Christian (9/25/09)...She accumulated 1313 minutes of action and had three points while helping anchor a defense that surrendered 1.58 points per game and assisted on four shutouts.
